headline: BlackRock Large Cap Focus Growth V.I. Fund Q4 2024 Commentary

headline: Netflix is the clear winner of the streaming war: MoffettNathanson
summary: The team at MoffettNathanson upgraded Netflix (NFLX) to a Buy rating while raising its price target to $1,100 per share, declaring that the company "has won the streaming wars" in an analyst note. MoffettNathanson senior analyst Robert Fishman — who wrote the note and declared Netflix the streaming victor — joins Madison Mills and ProShares global investment strategist Simeon Hyman for a conversation about the streaming platform's subscriber growth and ability to broadly source out content. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Catalysts here.
